because the pilot told him the craft was fine, USAir spokesman Richard 
Weintraub said Sunday. 
</P>
<P>
 Fox is a defendant in the lawsuit filed by Corboy on behalf of some victims' 
families, along with USAir and Boeing Co. 
</P>
<P>
 Weintraub said the jet had two routine preflight checks before taking off for 
Pittsburgh. 
</P>
<P>
