<P>
 The fight moved into the middle of the avenue, where an attacker shot the men. 
"Then he shot a 16-year-old girl who came to their aid," Lohman said. 
</P>
<P>
 Investigators were looking for a man believed to have fled in a dark blue, 
two-door 1993 or 1994 Honda Prelude. It had a "Hypertec Racing" decal across 
the top of the windshield, and the words "Powered by Honda Hypertec Racing" on 
the passenger seat window. 
