<TEXT>
<P>
 ABC will celebrate the 25th anniversary of its top-rated soap opera "All My 
Children" with a one-hour special in prime time on Jan. 5. Carol Burnett will 
host. 
</P>
<P>
 The program will feature clips of the show's most popular characters and story 
lines, plus interviews with fans and its current and former stars. 
</P>
