906 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
STREET SMART: TRAFFIC IS TOO LIGHT TO JUSTIFY COST OF A LEFT-TURN LANE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By SARA CATANIA, TIMES STAFF WRITER 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Dear Street Smart: 
</P>
<P>
 I've noticed on California 33 that there is a new left-turn lane for 
southbound traffic at Creek Lane near Oak View. 
</P>
<P>
 This had been a dangerous place to turn, so the lane is a welcome addition. 
</P>
<P>
