<P>
 Unemployment Tally Due to Be Released: The October jobless rate and local 
payroll employment statistics for Orange County are scheduled to be released 
today, and economy watchers say they are expecting the two reports to show at 
least a slight improvement in the county's job market. The most recent 
unemployment rate, for September, was 6% -- well below the statewide rate of 
8.2% but a tick up from the county's August jobless rate of 5.9%. 
</P>
